                            <note>The readings for this office are divided into three parts. 
                                The first part comprises: 1Thes 4, 15 - 5, 10; excerpts from 1Pet 2 and 5; Ac 16, 25-34; Mt 25, 1-13; Lev 23, 3f; 1Cor 15, 51 - 16, 1; 1Jn 1, 1-6; Ac 20, 6-12; Jn 3, 1-8. 
                                The second part comprises: Lk 1, 27-38; Jn 19, 25-27. 
                                The third part comprises: Eph 6, 10-24; 2Pet 3, 8-14; Ac 12, 6-11; Mk 13, 32-37; Nm 15, 32-36; Dn 9, 22-26; Ac 18, 1-4; Mk 13, 14-18; 2Cor 4, 7-10. 13-14; 1Jn 2, 27 - 3, 1; Ac 5, 27-32; Jn 20, 1-18.</note>
                        
