                                <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">Ownership Note</desc>
                                    <locus target="#60"/>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ዝመጽሐፈ፡ ዘአርከለዲስ፡ ንግዱ፡ ወብእሲቱ፡ ወለተ፡ ገብርኤል፡ ጣይቱ፡ ወውሉዱ፡ ወለተ፡ ሚካኤል፡ አዘነጋሽ፡ ዕሤተ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ወልደ፡ ኪሮስ፡ ወልደ፡ ማርያም፡ ወለተ፡ ማርያም፡ መክብበ፡ ሰማዕት።</q>
                                    <q xml:lang="en">This book belongs to ʾArkaladis Nǝgdu; his wife is Walatta Gabrǝʾel Ṭāytu; his sons are Walatta Mikāʾel ʾAzanagāš, ʿƎśeta Mikāʾel, Walda Kiros, Walda Māryām, Walatta Māryām, Makbǝba Samāʿǝt.</q>
                                    <p>The note states that <persName ref="PRS11029Arkala"/> is the owner of the book and mentions his relatives: his wife <persName ref="PRS11030WalattaG"/>, his sons and daughters <persName ref="PRS11031WalattaM"/>, <persName ref="PRS11032EsetaM"/>, <persName ref="PRS11033WaldaKi"/>, <persName ref="PRS11034WaldaMa"/>, <persName ref="PRS11035WalattaM"/>, and <persName ref="PRS11036Makbeba"/>.</p>
                                </item>
