                                    <q xml:lang="en">This book belongs to ʾArkaladis; his wife is Walatta Gabrǝʾel Ṭāytu Nǝgdu; </q>
                                    <p>The note states that <persName ref="PRS11029Arkala"/> is the owner of the book and mentions his wife <persName ref="PRS11030WalattaG"/>. 
